name: dustinleavins on GitHub
body:
### Welcome
This is dustinleavins's GitHub user page.

[dustinleavins's Profile on GitHub](https://github.com/dustinleavins)

### Repositories

[KSMVVM.WPF](https://github.com/dustinleavins/KSMVVM.WPF) - Kinda Small MVVM Framework for WPF

[LeavinsSoftware.CIB](https://github.com/dustinleavins/LeavinsSoftware.CIB) - Open-source repository for [CIB Collection Manager](http://www.leavins-software.com/collection/)

[Saltstorm](https://github.com/dustinleavins/saltstorm) - An open-source platform where people can "bet" play money on anything.

[SingleAppLauncher](https://github.com/dustinleavins/SingleAppLauncher) - .NET program that launches a single application. Intended for use with apps that auto-update.

[CalculatorD](https://github.com/dustinleavins/CalculatorD) - Basic calculator with graphical interface written in Java
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
